            type: "practitioner",
            painPoints: "[\"Alert storms of 200-400 raw alerts during market open swamp the queue every single day\", \"No automated correlation means manually reading alerts to find the root cause\", \"Context switching between monitoring dashboards, runbooks, and ticketing burns 30+ minutes per incident\", \"On-call fatigue from 3am pages that turn out to be noise\"]",
