            painPoints: "[\"AIOps adoption stalling because analysts don't trust correlation models they can't explain\", \"Difficult to prove ROI of ITOM investment to finance and the VP\", \"Runbooks are outdated and differ between analysts \\u2014 inconsistent response quality\", \"No visibility into which infrastructure changes caused alert spikes\"]",
